# macOS Virtualization Engine - Ignore List

# --- Core Binary Images (Heavy) ---
# Ignore virtual hard disks and macOS installers
*.qcow2
*.img
*.dmg
*.chunklist

# --- OS Specific ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# --- Logs & Temp ---
*.log
qemu.command
# NVRAM variables can sometimes be transient, but we keep the .fd files by default
# if you want to ignore user-specific NVRAM changes, uncomment below:
# OVMF_VARS.fd

# --- WSL / Linux specific ---
*.swp
*~
